transition to a free market economy. Last, but not least, our 
Azerbaijani brothers, headed by Mr. Aliyev, are determined to 
establish a pluralistic, participatory, and democratic system. 
All these factors have led us to look to the near future 
together with hope. The fact that our two states are joined in 
the ideal of democracy will add a new power to the strong ties 
between our two peoples. [end recording] 
  The Azerbaijani president said that the agreements will 
further advance the existing relations in all fields. 
  After this ceremony, Azerbaijani President Aliyev gave a 
