<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Energy, Natural Resources Under Secretary Resigns </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0802151794 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1440 GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA0802151794 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ankara, Feb 8 (AA) -- Mahir Barutcu, Energy and 
Natural Resources Ministry under secretary, resigned from his 
post, it was reported on Tuesday [8 February]. 
  Barutcu speaking to AA reporter on his resignation said he 
presented his resignation to the minister of energy and natural 
resources. 
  He said "I resigned because I did not approve certain 
appointments taking parts in the ministry." [as received] 
  Barutcu was appointed to the post on Dec 31, 1991. 

</TEXT>

