also thought that peacekeeping training was the only form of 
Finnish participation in the initial stage. According to 
Paasio, Sweden and Switzerland are very interested in the 
Partnership for Peace. Paasio thought it possible that at best 
the Partnership could be the beginning of a pan-European 
security system. 

